  "description": "A flavorful and healthy Canadian-inspired stir-fry dish featuring diced tomatoes, garlic, and a blend of spices, perfect for a light and satisfying meal. This low-sodium-friendly recipe is ideal for those looking for a guilt-free culinary experience.",
